pr_title: Changed editOrgModal from ant-design to material ui design and used React hooks to submit form.
pr_body:
<!--- Provide a general summary of your changes in the Title above -->
Changed editOrgModal from ant-design to material ui design and used React hooks to submit form.

## Description
<!--- Describe your changes in detail -->
* I have replaced ant-design to material ui design. 
* Used React hooks to submit form   
``` 
 const [formValue, setformValue] = React.useState({
    org_name: "",
    org_website: "",
    org_link_facebook: "",
    org_link_github: "",
    org_link_linkedin: "",
    org_link_twitter: "",
    org_description: "",
    org_country: "",
  });
```

```
const handleChange = (e) => {
    const { name, value } = e.target;
    setformValue((prev) => ({
      ...prev,
      [name]: value,
    }));
  };
```
